APKTool

1. Overview
Use Cases:
- Decompile Smali code
- تحليل resources & manifest
- إعادة ترجمة APK
- Reverse engineering للـ Android apps

---

2. Key Features
- Decode XML resources
- Decompile/compile Smali
- Framework handling
- Full rebuild support

----

3. Installation

 Linux
sudo apt install apktool

---

4. Common Commands
apktool d app.apk
apktool b app_folder
Resource files:
apktool d --only-main-classes app.apk

---

5. Important Parameters
Parameter	Description
d	Decompile APK
b	Build APK
--no-src	Ignore smali code
--only-main-classes	Faster decode
